<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٨٤ ... سُورَةُ الِانْشِقَاقِ ... آياتها ٢٥ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{انشَقَّتْ}</span> ... تَصَدَّعَتْ، وَتَفَطَّرَتْ بِالغَمَامِ يَوْمَ القِيَامَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا}</span> ... أَطَاعَتْ لِأَمْرِ رَبِّهَا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَحُقَّتْ}</span> ... وَحُقَّ لَهَا أَنْ تُطِيعَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُدَّتْ}</span> ... بُسِطَتْ، وَوُسِّعَتْ، وَدُكَّتْ جِبَالُهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَلْقَتْ}</span> ... قَذَفَتْ مَا فِي بَطْنِهَا مِنَ الأَمْوَاتِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كَادِحٌ إِلَى رَبِّكَ}</span> ... سَاعٍ إِلَى اللهِ، وَعَامِلٌ بِالخَيْرِ أَوِ الشَّرِّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كِتَابَهُ}</span> ... صَحِيفَةَ عَمَلِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{يَدْعُو ثُبُورًا}</span> ...<span class="c5"> يَدْعُو بِالهَلَاكِ قَائِلًا:</span> وَاثُبُورَاهْ!<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيَصْلَى سَعِيرًا}</span> ... يَدْخُلُ النَّارَ يُقَاسِي حَرَّهَا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لَّن يَحُورَ}</span> ... لَنْ يَرْجِعَ إِلَى اللهِ لِيُحَاسِبَهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَلَا أُقْسِمُ}</span> ... أُقْسِمُ، وَ <span class="c2">(لَا)</span>: لِتَاكِيدِ القَسَمِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِالشَّفَقِ}</span> ... بِاحْمِرَارِ الأُفُقِ عِنْدَ الغُرُوبِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(١٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَقَ}</span> ... جَمَعَ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اتَّسَقَ}</span> ... تَكَامَلَ نُورُهُ، وَأَبْدَرَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>